data.description: Welcome to this exquisite Garden Ridge masterpiece! Nestled in a picturesque community with spacious lots and a gated entry this home offers a country feel and a truly exceptional living experience. Built primarily as a one story with a floor plan that offers privacy as the split wings of the home separate multiple bedrooms.  The rock and stucco exterior perfectly fits the architecture.  A 4 car garage offers all of the parking you need as well as plenty of storage room.  As you step inside, you'll immediately be captivated by the open floor plan, where gleaming hardwood floors, vaulted ceilings, 8 ft doors, and generously sized rooms create a warm and inviting atmosphere. The living room features a stunning floor-to-ceiling stone fireplace, thoughtfully designed built-ins, a charming wood-beamed ceiling, and double glass doors leading to the covered patio. It's the perfect place to relax with loved ones, whether you're hosting gatherings or enjoying a cozy night by the fire.  The kitchen is a true dream, boasting stainless steel appliances, including double ovens, a built-in microwave, gas cooktop, stainless vent hood, and dimming lights. In addition, custom cabinets that go to the ceiling, and a spacious walk-in pantry providing ample storage and functionality. The adjacent breakfast area is not only perfect for casual dining, but also offers a buffet niche or even a piano if you desire. For more formal occasions, the dining room is a showstopper with its coffered ceiling and modern chandelier, setting the stage for memorable dinners and celebrations. A full butler's pantry with beverage refrigerator, wine storage, and plenty of counter space for serving.  Retreat to the primary owner's suite, a haven of luxury with outside access, a trey ceiling trimmed in crown molding, and a spa-like bath. The bath features a soaking tub, a separate walk-in shower, and double vanities, creating a serene space to unwind. But that's not all! The seller has thoughtfully added a covered patio, an additional two-car garage, a gym, storage space under stairs, two separate upstairs offices with its own AC/heating unit, a half bathroom, and a game recreation room. With a total of 5 bedrooms and 4.5 baths, there's plenty of space for everyone to enjoy their own private oasis. Outside you will appreciate the wrought iron fencing, LED lights, and the outdoor kitchen and sink perfect for outdoor fun!  Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
